title: Manufactured Goods, Imports for France
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1878-1887 (2)--Original Data, 1885-1939. Figures For 1878-1887 Are Not Strictly Comparable With 1885-1934 Data, But Are Taken From The Best Available Official Sources. Source: For 1878-1887 Inclusive, Bulletin De Statistique Et De Legislation Comparee (Finance Ministere) 1879 And Monthly.
